Long Island's Air and Space Museum. Over 75 air and space craft in 8 exhibit galleries, chronicling 100 years of aviation from hot air balloons to an actual lunar module. Located on Museum Row in Nassau County Long Island, NY, we are easily accessible via major roads and parking is always free.
